Episodes.Title: Episode 1
Episodes.Plot: While Cutter tries to make sense of Claudia's disappearance, another anomaly appears. Raptors are running wild through a shopping centre, and the team are called in to sort out the problem.
Episodes.GuestStars: James Murray (Stephen Hart), Hannah Spearritt (Abby Maitland), Karl Theobald (Oliver Leek)

Episodes.Title: Episode 2
Episodes.Plot: Bizarre shaped giant worms, some of which are large enough to consume a human are moving around in a strange fog.
Episodes.GuestStars: Karl Theobold (Oliver Leek), Naomi Bentley (Caroline Steel), Ruth Millar (Shelley), Jason Thorpe (Terry), Togo Igawa (Mr Nagata), Tim Faraday (le Nettoyeur)

Episodes.Title: Episode 3
Episodes.Plot: Nick Cutter and the rest of the ARC have to stop Sabre tooth tigers that are on the loose and are killing people at will.
Episodes.GuestStars: Karl Theobald (Oliver Leek), Naomi Bentley (Caroline Steel), Rory MacGregor (Kenny Johnson), Rory MacGregor (Kenny Johnson), Gillian Kearney (Valerie Irwin)

Episodes.Title: Episode 4
Episodes.Plot: A group of creatures called the mer slip into the city's canal system after floodwaters pour through an anomaly to the future.
Episodes.GuestStars: Jacob Anderson (Lucien), James Murray (Stephen Hart), Naomi Bentley (Caroline Steel)

Episodes.Title: Episode 5
Episodes.Plot: Giant scorpians are terrorising the team, and they find themselves in serious trouble.

Episodes.Title: Episode 6
Episodes.Plot: A woolly mammoth rampages across the M25 motorway.
Episodes.GuestStars: Ramon Tikaram (Mick), Susan Salmon (Dina), Oliver Coleman (Ed)

Episodes.Title: Episode 7
Episodes.Plot: The team have to deal with the return of the future predator along with other creatures.
Episodes.GuestStars: Naomi Bentley (Caroline Steel), Karl Theobald (Oliver Leek), Tim Faraday (le Nettoyeur), Claire Spence (Lorraine Wickes)
